<p>Follow these steps to set up and start using your blog:</p>
<ol id="help-intro">
    <li>
        <strong>Update your profile</strong> Once logged in, head to the <a href="{!! route('canvas.admin.profile.index') !!}">Edit Profile</a> page and update your information. You should
        also <a href="{!! route('canvas.admin.profile.privacy') !!}">update your password</a> to keep your blog as secure as possible.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Configure your website</strong> Visit the <a href="{!! route('canvas.admin.settings') !!}">Settings</a> page where you can
                                                customize and configure all the options for your site, even changing the theme from the default <strong>Paper</strong> to <strong>Dark Paper</strong>!
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Start posting content</strong> Finally, you can <a href="{!! route('canvas.admin.post.create') !!}">add new content</a> to your blog.
    </li>
</ol>

<small>For more information, refer to the specific topics listed in the next section or <a href="mailto:austin.todd.j@gmail.com">contact the author</a> for an urgent
question that you need answered.</small>